Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.63,0:00:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉又来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.53,0:00:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的一集马上就要开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.00,0:00:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了找齐四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.77,0:00:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了用这把铁碎牙打败奈落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.37,0:00:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与七人帮的战斗\N仍在继续进行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.27,0:00:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一场吊唁银骨的交战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.48,0:00:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炼骨千方百计
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.41,0:00:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想抢夺\N钢牙的四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.01,0:00:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师  珊瑚\N七宝跟云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.75,0:00:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿梭于时空\N发生在战国时代与现代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.92,0:00:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.25,0:00:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分散在蓝蓝天空上的 七颗星星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.03,0:00:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一颗星星 都刻着我的思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.10,0:00:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算梦想被粉碎 我也要寻找爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.04,0:00:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无处可逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.07,0:00:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧紧抓着我的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.08,0:00:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些骗人的光阴 我再也不会输给它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.25,0:01:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睁大眼睛 看清楚这瞬间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.86,0:01:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它仍然紧紧围绕着我们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.06,0:01:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人啜泣的 现实生活中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.07,0:01:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的…到底是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.30,0:01:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繁忙的这个世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.84,0:01:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永恒的碎片 忽隐又忽现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.08,0:01:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去触摸 去捕捉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.08,0:01:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.02,0:01:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了得到最后的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.03,0:01:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.79,0:02:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.10,0:02:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要用这家伙来收拾你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.84,0:02:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.90,0:02:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就送你上西天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.81,0:02:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.63,0:02:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  居然动不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.34,0:02:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.57,0:02:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银骨身上的四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.01,0:02:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是继续留在身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.74,0:03:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后恐怕\N会落入蛮骨大师兄手里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.34,0:03:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.01,0:03:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我再为那小子卖命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.56,0:03:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤口渐渐复原了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.63,0:03:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦死了  就什么都没了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.36,0:03:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  银骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.84,0:03:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.61,0:03:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好极了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.38,0:03:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在向大师兄报告之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.48,0:03:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要你先去一个地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.59,0:03:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙脚上的四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.09,0:03:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非抢过来不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.73,0:03:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第117话\N消失于火河中的坏蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.38,0:04:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算醒过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.54,0:04:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙少主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.74,0:04:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.25,0:04:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昏迷了整整一个晚上呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.62,0:04:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.18,0:04:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙少主\N你还记得发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.75,0:04:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫银骨的铁甲怪物\N爆炸的时候你受了伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.12,0:04:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.39,0:04:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.19,0:04:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大一股恶心臭味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.06,0:04:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.13,0:04:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全身都一股腥骚的狗臭味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.07,0:04:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉为了救你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.14,0:04:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特地把你\N背到这个地方来的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.34,0:04:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.07,0:04:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是戈薇大姐\N特地拜托他的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.21,0:04:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个家伙\N为什么不拦着戈薇呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.78,0:04:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们自己抬我不就行了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.98,0:04:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我们自己也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.41,0:04:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也都受了伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.78,0:04:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我说这种笨蛋\N随便把他扔在路边就算了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.92,0:04:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.79,0:04:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正打从开始我就不期待\N这家伙会道什么谢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.79,0:04:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.49,0:04:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么全身都湿透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.73,0:05:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还用问吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.30,0:05:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚狠狠洗了一个澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.10,0:05:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算洗掉\N身上那股恶心的臭狼味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.93,0:05:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.23,0:05:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好恶心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.87,0:05:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话应该我说才对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.44,0:05:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别发火嘛  钢牙少主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.31,0:05:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.51,0:05:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经把这家伙\N搬到安全的地方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.45,0:05:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来这笨蛋是死是活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.75,0:05:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我完全没有关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.18,0:05:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.75,0:05:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛说得这么绝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.75,0:05:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.82,0:05:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天到晚就知道教训我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.19,0:05:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙一句道谢的话都没有\N你为什么不骂骂他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.46,0:05:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道谢道谢的烦不烦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.46,0:05:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么想听的话我就说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.63,0:05:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.47,0:05:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次多亏有你\N我才能够逃过一劫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.34,0:05:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该谢的人是我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.14,0:05:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是负责运送而已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.71,0:05:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然人家已经恢复精神了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.78,0:05:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不用管他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.91,0:05:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是钢牙\N好像还是动不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.35,0:05:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你就不管\N弥勒还有珊瑚了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.22,0:05:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.42,0:05:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们两个人上了白灵山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.99,0:06:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不知道怎么样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.66,0:06:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多是时候\N该回去看一看了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.56,0:06:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.86,0:06:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.93,0:06:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是毒虫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.87,0:06:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们先在这边等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.37,0:06:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先把它解决掉\N免得回去通风报信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.82,0:06:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白角还有银太\N你们两个觉得怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.45,0:06:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一点点痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.59,0:06:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次真的被打得很惨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.09,0:06:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  药箱没有带出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.53,0:06:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有办法帮你们敷药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.19,0:06:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  快别这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.20,0:06:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇大姐有这份心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.03,0:06:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们两个就已经感激不尽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.40,0:06:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟钢牙很不一样\N这两个很有礼貌嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.91,0:06:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇你也闻到了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.55,0:06:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是感觉到一股\N四魂之玉碎片的气味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.98,0:07:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宝你说你闻到什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.98,0:07:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一股好浓的火药味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.63,0:07:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整条河…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.64,0:07:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.45,0:07:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.02,0:07:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.53,0:07:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.53,0:07:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.17,0:07:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是七人帮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.34,0:08:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经在河里倒了一堆油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.08,0:08:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你们往哪逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.24,0:08:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是炼骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.24,0:08:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.35,0:08:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然追来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.38,0:08:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙少主这里危险啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.35,0:08:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个臭家伙\N今天我要去宰了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.89,0:08:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙少主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.49,0:08:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万别动  钢牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.89,0:08:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经受了重伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.63,0:08:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看箭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.00,0:08:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.27,0:08:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.28,0:08:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.52,0:08:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炼骨这个家伙\N居然来得这么快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.75,0:08:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子是等不及\N死在我的刀下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.89,0:08:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.02,0:08:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,披上这个再走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.12,0:08:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  这件火鼠袍子耐得住火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.13,0:08:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留着给你们穿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.76,0:08:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还得\N保护那只瘦皮狼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.30,0:08:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要你插手多管闲事\N犬夜叉臭笨狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.67,0:09:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个坏蛋\N他要的是我的四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.54,0:09:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该由我来对付他才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.51,0:09:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这该死的  少在那里逞强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.67,0:09:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一你的\N四魂之玉碎片真的被抢走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.04,0:09:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时又是我倒霉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.18,0:09:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.78,0:09:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你要小心一点  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.82,0:09:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个坏蛋身上\N带着两块四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.58,0:09:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像比蛮骨还少嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.05,0:09:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉这小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.69,0:09:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么快就回来了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.32,0:09:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.39,0:09:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在山洞里舒不舒服啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.16,0:09:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少废话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.06,0:09:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上出去收拾你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.16,0:09:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.93,0:09:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样飞走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.23,0:09:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不会等你这臭小子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.80,0:09:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮筒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.70,0:09:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你会飞也跑不掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.44,0:09:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.55,0:09:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.05,0:09:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母的话  根本不怕火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.95,0:09:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好  云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.05,0:09:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样继续攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.09,0:09:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老子没那个闲功夫陪你玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.60,0:10:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母  到那家伙头顶上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.47,0:10:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧  炼骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.07,0:10:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.99,0:10:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.99,0:10:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.39,0:10:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇大姐  快点进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.76,0:10:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.77,0:10:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.02,0:11:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你们这一次\N能不被气爆烧死吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.90,0:11:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的了\N四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.77,0:11:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.01,0:11:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没人死掉啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.91,0:11:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要感恩喔  钢牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.68,0:11:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸亏戈薇刚刚\N把犬夜叉的袍子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.91,0:11:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,披在我们大家身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.92,0:11:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只臭笨狗的袍子\N我才不稀罕穿呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.69,0:11:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为这样就赢了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.42,0:11:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.06,0:11:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁赢谁输还不知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.06,0:11:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把你们炸成碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.53,0:11:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爆雷筒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.93,0:11:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你到底在想什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.20,0:11:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在山洞里面引爆\N连你自己都会完蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.07,0:11:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少废话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.07,0:11:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我已经没有退路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.94,0:11:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.21,0:11:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银骨留下来的四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.35,0:11:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我擅自使用没向大师兄报备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.31,0:12:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一让蛮骨知道\N他一定会杀了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.48,0:12:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全都知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.22,0:12:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把上次从那个\N叫做戈薇的女孩身上偷来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.32,0:12:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四魂之玉碎片给藏了起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.22,0:12:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先别发火  大师兄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.59,0:12:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原本就打算要交给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.33,0:12:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算你老实嘛  炼骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.40,0:12:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几个兄弟里面\N果然你的脑筋最灵光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.10,0:12:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.91,0:12:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望不要再有下一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.87,0:12:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.98,0:12:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你脚上的四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.41,0:12:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天无论如何我要定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.35,0:12:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.98,0:12:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.02,0:12:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上你那两块\N我一定可以打赢蛮骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.62,0:12:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是说说就算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.49,0:12:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是来真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.00,0:12:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为会有第二次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.37,0:12:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为自己可以逃过一劫吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.77,0:12:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.64,0:12:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有理由会死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.14,0:12:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我还有四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.54,0:13:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会死的就只有你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.45,0:13:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别得意忘形了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.32,0:13:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.82,0:13:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.25,0:13:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在  瘦皮狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.03,0:13:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.83,0:13:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没完呢  臭笨狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.03,0:13:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混帐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.41,0:13:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.18,0:13:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混帐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.05,0:13:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.70,0:13:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.07,0:13:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想应该很快就可以找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.43,0:14:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇大姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.20,0:14:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想犬夜叉\N一定是漂到岸边去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.34,0:14:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只臭笨狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.47,0:14:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会被炸成碎片了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.08,0:14:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.08,0:14:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙少主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.85,0:14:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就是嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.71,0:14:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且那个笨蛋…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.45,0:14:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉\N没有穿上这件火鼠袍子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.33,0:14:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这本来可以保护他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.46,0:14:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿…戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.70,0:14:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惹她哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.36,0:14:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别哭了好不好  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.47,0:14:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我害了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.74,0:14:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫我要穿上的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.24,0:14:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么能怪你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.74,0:14:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时我也看见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.11,0:14:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他自己硬要强迫塞给你的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.25,0:14:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.51,0:14:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁在强迫个鬼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.48,0:14:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.89,0:14:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你没事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.16,0:14:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身体构造\N可是与众不同的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.13,0:14:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.16,0:15:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炼骨那小子\N没想到他居然这么怕死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.06,0:15:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在引爆之前\N突然把手上的爆雷筒给扔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.07,0:15:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早知道会是这种结果了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.14,0:15:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜哪有那么容易死的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.41,0:15:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子  你再给我说一次看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.74,0:15:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想打架啊  是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.51,0:15:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我非一口气收拾你不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.25,0:15:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看看自己有多狼狈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.15,0:15:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想收拾我…\N犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.43,0:15:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢天谢地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.10,0:15:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有受伤吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.47,0:15:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要紧呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.67,0:15:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.94,0:15:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  让你担心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.81,0:15:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的…真的没事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.81,0:15:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙少主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.18,0:15:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道就这么算了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.98,0:15:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次就放过他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.49,0:16:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚差一点没吓坏戈薇呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.06,0:16:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我警告你  臭笨狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.69,0:16:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为这样就算赢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.19,0:16:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对戈薇是绝对不会死心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.20,0:16:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早就输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.80,0:16:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你没有眼睛看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.97,0:16:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.34,0:16:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过就随便抱了一下嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.84,0:16:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好大惊小怪的  笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.21,0:16:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不甘心是不是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.34,0:16:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活该  快滚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.94,0:16:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.81,0:16:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉\N想哭的感觉渐渐消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.08,0:16:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直骂人家笨蛋\N自己才是笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.59,0:16:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  两个都是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.05,0:16:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直是笨蛋二人组
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.73,0:16:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.29,0:16:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭不出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.91,0:16:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也是  什么都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.31,0:16:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连妖怪的迹象也没有呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.55,0:17:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过奈落\N跟七人帮之间一定有所关联
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.12,0:17:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而白心上人暗中保护七人帮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.75,0:17:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.99,0:17:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就不知道原因是什么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.79,0:17:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然白心上人是在帮助奈落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.19,0:17:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在白灵山布下结界的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.80,0:17:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么奈落躲在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.03,0:17:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个推论也很合理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.63,0:17:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  一起上山顶看看再说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.20,0:17:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是查不到任何线索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.30,0:17:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也无法向犬夜叉交代了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.80,0:17:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.14,0:17:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.04,0:17:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些结界还真要命呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.31,0:17:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得可以跟你单独相处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.78,0:17:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然…绑手绑脚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.35,0:17:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去的话…又会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.86,0:17:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.57,0:17:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  又失败了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.54,0:17:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一次又没抢到\N钢牙的四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.77,0:18:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一我擅自使用\N银骨的四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.24,0:18:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事穿帮的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.05,0:18:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛮骨一定会宰了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.52,0:18:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底该怎么办呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.79,0:18:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最猛胜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.14,0:18:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛮…蛮骨大师兄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.61,0:18:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炼骨  那些小虫告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.61,0:18:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银骨那小子已经死了是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.21,0:18:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是可惜呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.88,0:18:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你费了那么大的力气\N才把银骨改造得那么完美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.62,0:18:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也算不幸中的大幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.39,0:18:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少你还能活下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.23,0:18:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对付杀生丸的睡骨也死了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.93,0:19:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡骨他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.57,0:19:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.14,0:19:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟七人当中只剩下\N我跟你还有蛇骨三个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.54,0:19:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.41,0:19:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后我们得加倍团结才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.18,0:19:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.25,0:19:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛮骨这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.12,0:19:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道没发现银骨的碎片吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.66,0:19:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.33,0:19:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子我还没玩完呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.27,0:19:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算暂时保住这条命了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.18,0:19:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.95,0:19:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面的路…好像突然断了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.35,0:19:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像\N有人故意劈断的一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.46,0:19:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师  你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.99,0:20:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.90,0:20:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子\N路好像一直延续到山洞里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.60,0:20:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.97,0:20:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,办得到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.20,0:20:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试试看就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.17,0:20:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.72,0:20:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.39,0:20:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师  抓住绳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.13,0:20:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真有两下子呢  珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.44,0:20:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以一直通到里面呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.94,0:20:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎有一股邪气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.75,0:20:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧  珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.01,0:20:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有错\N奈落一定躲在这里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.93,0:21:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.57,0:21:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底打算\N把我关在这种地方多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.07,0:21:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.01,0:21:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是神无啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.44,0:21:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我还真羡慕你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.28,0:21:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身上完全没有妖气\N可以自由进出圣地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.02,0:21:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起你来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.32,0:21:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要离开这里一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.79,0:21:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会被可恨的圣地给消灭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.06,0:21:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.20,0:21:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.00,0:21:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.10,0:21:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法师跟驱魔师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.81,0:21:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下可好玩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.21,0:22:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没有大展拳脚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.52,0:22:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷亲你一下 装作若无其事的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.26,0:22:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这样调皮 是不是像个孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.73,0:22:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早已习惯 被你说是娇嗔无理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.87,0:22:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 「喜欢你」 这三个字却始终说不出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.31,0:22:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Sweet Emotion
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.55,0:22:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对着镜子 多看一次 看看自己的微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.16,0:22:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想飞奔出去追求刺激就得挺起胸膛向前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.17,0:23:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大胆放手去做 直到满意为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.92,0:23:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷亲你一下 装作若无其事的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.79,0:23:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这样调皮 是不是像个孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.16,0:23:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早已习惯 被你说是娇嗔无理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.37,0:23:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 「喜欢你」 这三个字却始终说不出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.64,0:23:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Sweet Emotion
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.42,0:23:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白灵山圣地里居然有妖气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.63,0:23:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落一定就躲在里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.19,0:23:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的来了\N两个血肉之躯的凡人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.96,0:23:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.73,0:23:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也算得上胆大包天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.43,0:23:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天谁也别想活着离开这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.03,0:23:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是奈落的毒虫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.20,0:23:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.97,0:23:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吸它们的话会中毒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.14,0:23:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了心爱的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.71,0:23:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算赴汤蹈火\N拼了这条命也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.21,0:24:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.44,0:24:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.94,0:24:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白灵山里面又里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.95,0:24:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚  对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.21,0:24:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你答应我一定要好好活下去



